Use the following rules for decision:

Green (Approved)
  - 10th marks ≥ 80%  
  - 12th marks ≥ 75%  
  - No year gap  
  - Annual income ≤ ₹2.4 lakh  

Amber (Pending - Manual Review Required)
  - 10th marks ≥ 80%  
  - 12th marks ≥ 75%  
  - Gap up to 2 years (must justify reason)  
  - Income between ₹2.4 – ₹5 lakh  
  - OR family members &gt; 7 OR medical issue mentioned  

Red (Rejected)
  - Fails to meet Green or Amber criteria  
  - Income above ₹5 lakh  
  - Marks below thresholds  
  - Gap &gt; 2 years (unjustified)  

Now, use the details provided below to make a decision.

Student Academic Details (from PDFs contains 3 documents 10th,12th marksheet and family income certificate)
{!$Input:PDF_parsed}

 Application Details 
