Income tone (e.g., “low-income,” “moderate,” “financial hardship”)
Whether income is proportionate to dependents
Whether income source suggests stability or instability
Example:
 
 ₹7 lakh for a family of 7 is inadequate →will be Green
 ₹7 lakh for a family of  3 is acceptable → likely Amber/Green


